ab: animation: bounce 1s infinite;@keyframes bounce {  0%, 100% {    transform: translateY(-25%);    animation-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.8, 0, 1, 1);  }  50% {    transform: translateY(0);    animation-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0, 0, 0.2, 1);  }}
ap: animation: ping 1s cubic-bezier(0, 0, 0.2, 1) infinite;@keyframes ping {  75%, 100% {    transform: scale(2);    opacity: 0;  }}
apb: animation: pulse 2s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.6, 1) infinite;@keyframes pulse {  0%, 100% {    opacity: 1;  }  50% {    opacity: .5;  }}
as: animation: spin 1s linear infinite;@keyframes spin {  from {    transform: rotate(0deg);  }  to {    transform: rotate(360deg);  }}
ff: font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, "Liberation Mono", "Courier New", monospace;
ffu: font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";
ffus: font-family: ui-serif, Georgia, Cambria, "Times New Roman", Times, serif;
ps: position: static;width: auto;height: auto;padding: 0;margin: 0;overflow: visible;clip: auto;white-space: normal;
tp: transition-property: color, background-color, border-color, text-decoration-color, fill, stroke, opacity, box-shadow, transform, filter, backdrop-filter;transition-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);transition-duration: 150ms;
tpc: transition-property: color, background-color, border-color, text-decoration-color, fill, stroke;transition-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);transition-duration: 150ms;
